      <h2 id="2. 쯈ue es Pandas?">2. 쯈u칠 es Pandas?<a class="anchor-link" href="#2. 쯈ue es Pandas?"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 2" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
